Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.50,0:01:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.97,0:01:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 明天大家一起去哪渡假吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.24,0:01:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.78,0:01:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得的黃金假期卻沒安排什麼節目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.85,0:01:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那多無聊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.38,0:01:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得嘛 一起出去走走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.82,0:01:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然說些莫名其妙的話 你是不是醉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.06,0:01:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這個人是千杯不醉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.73,0:01:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正你從來也沒清醒過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.13,0:01:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走啦 走啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.33,0:01:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以去草摩的別墅或借住渡假屋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.47,0:01:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不好啦 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.47,0:01:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.34,0:02:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了 我已經去洗過一次溫泉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.11,0:02:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是那一次我沒去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.81,0:02:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實說我也很想去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.38,0:02:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好羨慕妳喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.15,0:02:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.82,0:02:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別操縱她！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.19,0:02:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道 知道…所以說你們也會去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.56,0:02:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們不可能讓我跟小透兩人單獨相處吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.56,0:02:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過想讓我們獨處也可以 我不介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.57,0:02:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就這麼決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.24,0:02:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱們去渡假吧 我負責開車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.64,0:02:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.31,0:02:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紫吳 你有駕照嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.75,0:02:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該有吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.98,0:02:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛還要想呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.22,0:02:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 我們決定去草摩的別墅渡假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.96,0:02:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本是波鳥開車嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.06,0:02:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 這裡有個湖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.10,0:03:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮、好大喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.93,0:03:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湖值得妳這麼大驚小怪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.47,0:03:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 因為這是我第一次親眼看到湖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.17,0:03:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這別墅好像會有"傑森"出沒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.34,0:03:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又說這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.18,0:03:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說傑森…嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.98,0:03:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑森 傑森是什麼來著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.89,0:03:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的傑森就是新種的熊 孤陋寡聞的阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.96,0:03:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事誰不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.73,0:03:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.09,0:03:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是外國種的熊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.37,0:03:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是紫吳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.07,0:03:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛突然提出要來這裡渡假呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.20,0:03:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想不透這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.27,0:03:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八成有什麼目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.44,0:03:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是討厭 你們太疑神疑鬼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.71,0:03:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的只是想跟大家出來旅行罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.62,0:03:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到居然會被懷疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.98,0:03:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有空懷疑別人不如帶小透去湖邊散步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.72,0:04:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希、阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.49,0:04:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}靜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.10,0:04:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？你們倆怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.43,0:04:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氣氛很怪哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.93,0:04:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我一個人也無妨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.04,0:04:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來這裡需要一個開朗的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.71,0:04:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 叫綾女來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.81,0:04:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敢叫他來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.94,0:04:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就讓你下地獄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.02,0:04:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請慢走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.32,0:04:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打一開始就乖乖去散步不就得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.99,0:04:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紫吳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.96,0:04:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.66,0:04:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於你這次突然提出要渡假的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.03,0:04:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會又想欺負催稿人了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.57,0:04:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出去旅行 請別找我 草摩紫吳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.21,0:04:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個混蛋～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.88,0:04:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有欺負她 只是捉弄她一下罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.21,0:04:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是可憐的催稿人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.39,0:05:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我突然覺得氣氛好僵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.93,0:05:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩人連鬥嘴都沒興致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.37,0:05:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是在生我的氣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.30,0:05:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是為什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.64,0:05:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是去掃墓時我說錯什麼話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.05,0:05:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或做錯什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.72,0:05:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩人都很體貼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.68,0:05:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不忍心開口罵我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.35,0:05:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.19,0:05:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.92,0:05:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.56,0:05:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我實在是太粗心 完全沒有注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.10,0:05:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管我做錯什麼請你們儘管說出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.27,0:05:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 妳說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.70,0:05:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 妳莫名其妙在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.04,0:05:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾 阿夾你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.44,0:05:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 這是什麼爛路啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.38,0:06:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個腳印…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.02,0:06:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是傑森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.59,0:06:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？傑森！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.45,0:06:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都說了是熊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.95,0:06:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 糟糕 完了 很危險啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.62,0:06:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們得趕快回去 啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.13,0:06:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.83,0:06:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.77,0:06:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 沒問題 稿子已經好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.70,0:06:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.14,0:06:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大師 拜託你 我求你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.24,0:06:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我知道了 我掛電話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.41,0:06:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經打給編輯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.78,0:06:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來就該這麼做 別哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.82,0:06:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多無趣啊 這樣不好玩啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.75,0:06:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得不好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.76,0:06:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.22,0:06:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.49,0:06:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.99,0:06:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 妳有沒有受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.60,0:06:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.80,0:06:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 拜託妳好好注意腳下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.47,0:06:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.03,0:06:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去撿衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.71,0:07:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.81,0:07:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.31,0:07:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼好好注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.28,0:07:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一個摔跤的人憑什麼說這種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.39,0:07:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還敢吐槽我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.39,0:07:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次摔得最慘的人是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.96,0:07:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說養尊處優的少爺最沒路用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.89,0:07:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總比每天在山裡修行卻完全派不上用場的笨蛋來得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.36,0:07:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.63,0:07:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才修行四個月怎麼可能完全瞭解山裡的情形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.53,0:07:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換做是你兩天就曝屍荒野了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.84,0:07:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用這個機會好好學著點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.81,0:07:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這隻笨貓沒資格叫我學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.91,0:07:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁這個機會告訴你啊 傑森不是熊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.21,0:07:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是恐怖片裡的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.85,0:07:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你少在那邊不懂裝懂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.81,0:07:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖片裡出現的熊有什麼了不起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.75,0:07:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是有夠白痴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.45,0:07:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.62,0:07:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天非幹掉你不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.63,0:07:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早就聽膩這句台詞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.43,0:08:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有種別躲在樹上 下來和我對決吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.67,0:08:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.63,0:08:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就目前的體格而言 你比我卑鄙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.54,0:08:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽你在那邊胡說 居然叫這麼多同伙來助陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.71,0:08:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒辦法呀 是他們自己要來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.01,0:08:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是遺憾 看來這座山裡沒有你的伙伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.95,0:08:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 所以我說老鼠最賊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.85,0:08:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個真的很愛吵呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.20,0:08:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.50,0:08:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.80,0:08:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.00,0:08:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們吵得正兇 我卻笑了 實在太失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.81,0:08:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…我總算安心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.61,0:08:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們終於恢復過去的模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.75,0:08:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想到這裡我總算放心 就忍不住笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.35,0:08:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.16,0:09:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.23,0:09:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳剛剛摔跤前所說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.57,0:09:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我們並沒有生妳的氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.60,0:09:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們看起來像生氣的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.64,0:09:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實只是不太順罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.47,0:09:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.61,0:09:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣能在一起 感覺上好自然好理所當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.38,0:09:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己也是在不知不覺中慢慢依賴起妳來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.06,0:09:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你千萬別這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.29,0:09:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 已經沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.96,0:09:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 讓妳擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.74,0:09:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 我也沒在生氣喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.27,0:09:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.81,0:09:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是我也一樣不太順罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.41,0:09:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說你腦子不順嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.88,0:09:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少囉唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.56,0:10:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.99,0:10:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.29,0:10:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才是呢 一個人胡思亂想把事情鬧這麼大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.67,0:10:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我現在真的好開心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.07,0:10:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…你們不順 我不該說高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.51,0:10:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 像這樣大家在一起 感覺上好自然好理所當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.98,0:10:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也因這樣覺得不順時就讓它不順吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.52,0:10:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後也是 如果你們覺得不順那就讓它不順
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.69,0:10:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…這麼說也很奇怪喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.19,0:10:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換句話說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.02,0:10:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說你們不順是好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.33,0:10:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是說你們都很好沒什麼改變 這件事情很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.80,0:10:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.83,0:10:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼改變的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.70,0:10:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了愈來愈討厭這傢伙之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.47,0:10:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.71,0:10:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才是 剛剛說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.27,0:11:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這輩子都討厭你 死都討厭你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.34,0:11:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是感激你呀 我跟你同感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.59,0:11:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.09,0:11:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.43,0:11:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到他們吵架我卻說好 這話說起來也很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.60,0:11:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 天都快黑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.74,0:11:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 明天再去湖邊散步吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.07,0:11:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.08,0:11:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 準備好了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.92,0:11:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 都準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.65,0:11:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去湖邊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.12,0:11:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可別掉到湖裡喔 阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.26,0:11:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能掉進去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.39,0:11:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥先生 我們出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.14,0:12:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 波鳥睡著了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.81,0:12:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.44,0:12:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥也會睡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.98,0:12:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾 只要是人都需要睡眠的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.25,0:12:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事我也知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.58,0:12:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想說的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.85,0:12:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙不像會在人前睡覺的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.59,0:12:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說的倒也是啊 真是罕見啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.86,0:12:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來波鳥在本家承受的壓力不小啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.46,0:12:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 請蓋這條毯子 否則會感冒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.97,0:12:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透真是體貼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.77,0:12:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對能當個賢妻良母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.70,0:12:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我哪有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.61,0:12:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋紫吳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.24,0:12:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開口讚美別人是個美德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.08,0:12:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈 大家怎麼了 突然都呆住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.62,0:12:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你突然現身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.45,0:12:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 毫無徵兆 到底從哪裡冒出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.76,0:12:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這還用問嗎 當然是從門走進來的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.63,0:12:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾真是名符其實的大白癡呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.46,0:13:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 你最沒資格說我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.93,0:13:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 綾女你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.37,0:13:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 危險 別靠近他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.87,0:13:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位 很高興看到你們因跟我重逢流下感動之淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.91,0:13:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是請你們稍微冷靜一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.61,0:13:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是得某人的協助才能站在這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.58,0:13:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,某人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.41,0:13:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是我呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.58,0:13:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 紫吳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.85,0:13:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使全天下人都視你為敵 我也會站在你這一邊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.86,0:13:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾女 你才是我心靈的支柱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.03,0:13:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你 我的愛 祝你順風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.20,0:13:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你 我的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.03,0:13:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}法語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.70,0:13:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都說了 你到底是來幹嘛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.83,0:13:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先冷靜點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.60,0:13:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,某部校園片裡的老師也曾說過吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.07,0:13:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"人"這個字是由兩人互相扶持所構成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.88,0:13:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.88,0:13:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是句好對白啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.89,0:13:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只是想說說看而已嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.52,0:13:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好累喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.12,0:14:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有你在 真的很累人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.39,0:14:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事就回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.39,0:14:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.33,0:14:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.50,0:14:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當然永遠都有事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.20,0:14:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.33,0:14:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天就讓我們兄弟之情更加深入吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.57,0:14:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前 我會先讓你沉入湖底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.11,0:14:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 這樣啊 咱們兄弟將形影相隨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.08,0:14:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還是一個人去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.15,0:14:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.18,0:14:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是叫你別造成別人的困擾嗎 綾女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.85,0:14:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥先生 你醒了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.39,0:14:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵成這樣 我怎麼可能睡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 波鳥 早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.93,0:14:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉 吵醒你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.56,0:14:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也叫自己安靜點的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.97,0:14:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是吵死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.00,0:14:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為何會來這裡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.54,0:14:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.24,0:14:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去本家後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.54,0:14:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個53歲的工人告訴我 你跟大家一起來別墅渡假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.74,0:14:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣 那我也想參與 所以就來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.18,0:14:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼跟來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.18,0:14:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.02,0:15:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在波鳥面前說話就這麼坦誠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.99,0:15:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希、阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.25,0:15:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們今天不是要帶小透去湖邊散步的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.56,0:15:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.26,0:15:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.06,0:15:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.16,0:15:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎 既然如此 那就快點去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.00,0:15:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖不知道你們在磨蹭什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.34,0:15:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但既然要保護女性就該更機靈點才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.11,0:15:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不都是你這傢伙害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.91,0:15:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就去湖邊散步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.82,0:15:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是群麻煩的年輕人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.09,0:15:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你一定會跟去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.29,0:15:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊 紫吳 我才沒那麼不通情理呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.66,0:15:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且好久沒三個人聚一聚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.50,0:15:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 今晚我不會讓你睡的 紫吳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.50,0:15:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾女 這是我的榮幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.74,0:15:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到今晚可以跟你做同樣的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.91,0:15:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.47,0:15:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼老玩不膩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.98,0:16:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好清爽喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.59,0:16:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.49,0:16:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙今晚要睡這裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.26,0:16:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是你老哥 你想辦法處理吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.69,0:16:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能的話我早做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.70,0:16:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最討厭那種只知道靠別人的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.67,0:16:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你呢 還不是老靠著紫吳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.70,0:16:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事跟你無關吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.17,0:16:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說的好像你都知道似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.94,0:16:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才懶得知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.98,0:16:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你老在我面前晃 我不想看到你都不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.95,0:16:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你不會消失嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.22,0:16:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很想消失啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.02,0:16:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我為何非得跟你來湖邊不可呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.15,0:16:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 跟你來湖邊對我而言是件多痛苦的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.26,0:16:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼！這種地方多無聊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.30,0:16:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.93,0:16:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.53,0:16:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳可別誤會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.20,0:16:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.80,0:16:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們並不討厭來湖邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.34,0:17:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是討厭跟這傢伙來罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.44,0:17:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.27,0:17:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.51,0:17:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…那就好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.15,0:17:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要妳沒誤會就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.85,0:17:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.12,0:17:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在湖邊繞一圈好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.70,0:17:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.96,0:17:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.53,0:17:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.83,0:17:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.07,0:17:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照片 是佳菜婚禮的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.61,0:17:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看或不看是你的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.34,0:17:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.25,0:17:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她結婚了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.95,0:17:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然說要來別墅 我還以為怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.72,0:17:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼一回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.62,0:17:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你擔心了 不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.62,0:17:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直覺得應該告訴你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.03,0:18:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你衝到婚禮上從新郎手中把佳菜搶過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.10,0:18:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 紫吳說不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.64,0:18:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經挽回不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.01,0:18:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟佳菜已經結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.41,0:18:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 這照片也不看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無法接受這個結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.39,0:18:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是站在波鳥這一邊的人 所以有話直說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.56,0:18:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無法接受這樣的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.06,0:18:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佳菜太卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.79,0:18:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她可以忘記一切 捉住自己的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.00,0:18:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你呢 卻得揹負所有的不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.14,0:18:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你被她遺棄 被她利用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.11,0:18:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.31,0:18:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.95,0:18:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳覺得等雪融化之後會變成什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.89,0:19:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.29,0:19:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會變成春天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.40,0:19:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不全然是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.37,0:19:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你實在是太溫柔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.47,0:19:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說這也是你的優點 但你太體貼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.91,0:19:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因為這樣才老受些不必要受的罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.54,0:19:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會叫你跟佳菜破鏡重圓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.25,0:19:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我敢拍胸脯的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.52,0:19:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能讓你得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.75,0:19:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比佳菜還多一千倍、兩千倍的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.66,0:19:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種強勢的態度真該讓由希看看才對呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.40,0:19:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.50,0:19:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次若能認識一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.27,0:19:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一起時也不會覺得孤單的對象就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.87,0:19:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能在一起就等於幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.98,0:19:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是紫吳 有詩人的氣質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.54,0:19:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小說家 小說家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.41,0:19:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新的對象啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.52,0:20:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對被詛咒的十二生肖的人而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.72,0:20:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個願望可能有點無理吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.69,0:20:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了…\N他們回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.23,0:20:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔細想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.46,0:20:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能跟佳菜有這麼一段情 我也該心滿意足了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.80,0:20:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我而言這樣就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.21,0:20:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我唯一能做的就是希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.91,0:20:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別讓他們跟我有相同的遭遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.78,0:20:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你們回來了 由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.79,0:20:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他伙伴們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.42,0:20:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰是他的伙伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.72,0:20:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.16,0:20:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.39,0:20:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛我接受了波鳥的建議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.39,0:20:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後要用強勢的態度和你加深感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.06,0:20:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.33,0:20:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫強勢的態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.87,0:20:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 由希是我弟弟 我是由希的哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.07,0:20:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是個事實 我要在此向大家宣言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.74,0:21:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希 你必須服從我這個哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.38,0:21:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇～～～～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.35,0:21:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾女那傢伙還是沒搞懂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.66,0:21:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還是沒搞懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.20,0:21:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.03,0:21:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！！怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.00,0:21:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位 綾女變成一條蛇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.07,0:21:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西丟了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.61,0:21:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然對變成蛇的綾女感到有點抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.31,0:21:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過引起這樣的騷動 我真的很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.72,0:21:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我多希望這種愉快的日子能一直持續下去啊
